node.title: Diver missing at popular surf break off Margaret River coast
node.alt: Jay Davies rides the Box during round three at the Margaret River Pro, 2015
node.description: Authorities launch an air and sea search for a diver missing at The Box surf break off the Margaret River coast.
node.content: ["Police are appealing for help to find a missing diver who was last seen at a popular surfing spot in Margaret River, in Western Australia's south-west.", "An air and sea\u00a0search is underway to find the man, who is described as being in his mid-30s with long, dark hair.", "He was last seen wearing a black wetsuit and camouflage diving fins.", "It is\u00a0believed the man entered the water at around midday today, local time, at a surfing spot\u00a0known as The Box.", "More to come."]
